title: What I Value About Chinese Culture.
description: The account of my unexpected departure from Laos (to Yunnan, China) is alluded to in this video.  One short set of reflections on this can be found here: http://a-bas-le-ciel.blogspot.ca/2012/09/No-Nostalgia-for-Laos.html
